    "A %@ tonight tends to line up with about %@ higher on tomorrow’s %@ for you, based on %lld of your %@ days.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "%1$@ heute Nacht geht bei dir tendenziell mit etwa %2$@ mehr beim morgigen %3$@ einher, basierend auf %4$lld deiner %5$@ Tage."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "new",
            "value": "A %1$@ tonight tends to line up with about %2$@ higher on tomorrow’s %3$@ for you, based on %4$lld of your %5$@ days."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un %@ esta noche tiende a coincidir con alrededor de %@ más en tu %@ de mañana, según %lld de tus %@ días."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un %1$@ stanotte tende a corrispondere per te a circa %2$@ in più sul %3$@ di domani, sulla base di %4$lld dei tuoi %5$@ giorni."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "对你来说，今晚的%@往往对应高出约 %@ 的明日%@，依据是你 %lld 天（共 %@ 天）的数据。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "今晚的%@，往往對應著高出約 %@ 的明日%@，依據是你 %lld / %@ 天的資料。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A %@ tonight tends to line up with about %@ higher on tomorrow’s %@ for you, based on typical patterns.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "%1$@ heute Nacht geht bei dir tendenziell mit etwa %2$@ mehr beim morgigen %3$@ einher, basierend auf typischen Mustern."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "new",
            "value": "A %1$@ tonight tends to line up with about %2$@ higher on tomorrow’s %3$@ for you, based on typical patterns."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un %@ esta noche tiende a coincidir con alrededor de %@ más en tu %@ de mañana, según patrones típicos."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un %1$@ stanotte tende a corrispondere per te a circa %2$@ in più sul %3$@ di domani, in base a schemi tipici."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "对你来说，今晚的%@往往对应高出约 %@ 的明日%@，基于典型模式。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "今晚的%@，往往對應著高出約 %@ 的明日%@，這是依據一般模式得出的。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A %@ tonight tends to line up with about %@ lower on tomorrow’s %@ for you, based on %lld of your %@ days.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "%1$@ heute Nacht geht bei dir tendenziell mit etwa %2$@ weniger beim morgigen %3$@ einher, basierend auf %4$lld deiner %5$@ Tage."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "new",
            "value": "A %1$@ tonight tends to line up with about %2$@ lower on tomorrow’s %3$@ for you, based on %4$lld of your %5$@ days."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un %@ esta noche tiende a coincidir con alrededor de %@ menos en tu %@ de mañana, según %lld de tus %@ días."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un %1$@ stanotte tende a corrispondere per te a circa %2$@ in meno sul %3$@ di domani, sulla base di %4$lld dei tuoi %5$@ giorni."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "对你来说，今晚的%@往往对应低出约 %@ 的明日%@，依据是你 %lld 天（共 %@ 天）的数据。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "今晚的%@，往往對應著低出約 %@ 的明日%@，依據是你 %lld / %@ 天的資料。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A %@ tonight tends to line up with about %@ lower on tomorrow’s %@ for you, based on typical patterns.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "%1$@ heute Nacht geht bei dir tendenziell mit etwa %2$@ weniger beim morgigen %3$@ einher, basierend auf typischen Mustern."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "new",
            "value": "A %1$@ tonight tends to line up with about %2$@ lower on tomorrow’s %3$@ for you, based on typical patterns."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un %@ esta noche tiende a coincidir con alrededor de %@ menos en tu %@ de mañana, según patrones típicos."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un %1$@ stanotte tende a corrispondere per te a circa %2$@ in meno sul %3$@ di domani, in base a schemi tipici."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "对你来说，今晚的%@往往对应低出约 %@ 的明日%@，基于典型模式。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "今晚的%@，往往對應著低出約 %@ 的明日%@，這是依據一般模式得出的。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A 60-second snapshot of your beat-to-beat (R-R) intervals from the strap, cleaned (range and ectopic-beat filtering) before computing RMSSD the same way your overnight HRV is computed.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Eine 60-Sekunden-Momentaufnahme deiner Herzschlag-Intervalle (R-R) vom Strap, bereinigt (Bereichs- und Extrasystolen-Filterung), bevor RMSSD genauso berechnet wird wie deine nächtliche HRV."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Una instantánea de 60 segundos de tus intervalos latido a latido (R-R) desde la pulsera, depurada (filtrado de rango y de latidos ectópicos) antes de calcular el RMSSD de la misma forma en que se calcula tu VFC nocturna."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un'istantanea di 60 secondi degli intervalli battito-battito (R-R) dalla fascia, ripuliti (filtraggio di intervallo e battiti ectopici) prima di calcolare l'RMSSD nello stesso modo in cui viene calcolata la tua HRV notturna."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "来自手环的 60 秒逐拍（R-R）间期快照，在计算 RMSSD 之前经过清洗（范围和异位搏动过滤），计算方式与你的夜间 HRV 相同。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "來自手環的 60 秒逐拍（R-R）間期快照，在計算 RMSSD 之前經過清洗（範圍和異位搏動過濾），計算方式與你的夜間 HRV 相同。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A WHOOP export backfills recovery, strain, sleep and workouts. Apple Health can add HR, HRV, sleep, SpO₂, steps, workouts and weight.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ein WHOOP-Export füllt Erholung, Belastung, Schlaf und Workouts rückwirkend auf. Apple Health kann HF, HRV, Schlaf, SpO₂, Schritte, Workouts und Gewicht ergänzen."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Una exportación de WHOOP rellena recuperación, esfuerzo, sueño y entrenamientos. Apple Health puede añadir FC, VFC, sueño, SpO₂, pasos, entrenamientos y peso."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un'esportazione WHOOP ricostruisce recupero, carico, sonno e allenamenti. Apple Health può aggiungere FC, HRV, sonno, SpO₂, passi, allenamenti e peso."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "WHOOP 导出文件可回填恢复、强度、睡眠和锻炼。Apple Health 可补充心率、HRV、睡眠、SpO₂、步数、锻炼和体重。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "WHOOP 匯出可回填恢復、強度、睡眠與訓練。Apple Health 則可補充心率、HRV、睡眠、SpO₂、步數、訓練與體重。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A WHOOP membership runs $300–480 a year, for life. NOOP does this for free: one person, no servers, no subscription.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Eine WHOOP-Mitgliedschaft kostet 300–480 $ im Jahr, lebenslang. NOOP macht das kostenlos: eine Person, keine Server, kein Abo."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Una membresía de WHOOP cuesta entre $300 y $480 al año, de por vida. NOOP hace esto gratis: una sola persona, sin servidores, sin suscripción."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un abbonamento WHOOP costa 300–480 $ all'anno, a vita. NOOP lo fa gratis, una persona, nessun server, nessun abbonamento."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "WHOOP 会员资格每年 300–480 美元，终身如此。NOOP 免费做到这一点，一个人，没有服务器，没有订阅。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "WHOOP 會員資格每年 300–480 美元，終身如此。NOOP 免費做到這一點，一個人，沒有伺服器，沒有訂閱。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A badge shows whether a number was scored on-device by NOOP, or imported from Whoop or Apple Health.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ein Badge zeigt, ob ein Wert von NOOP auf dem Gerät berechnet oder aus Whoop bzw. Apple Health importiert wurde."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Una insignia muestra si un número fue calculado en el dispositivo por NOOP, o importado desde Whoop o Apple Health."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un badge indica se un numero è stato calcolato sul dispositivo da NOOP o importato da Whoop o Apple Health."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "徽章会标明某个数字是由 NOOP 在设备上计算的，还是从 Whoop 或 Apple Health 导入的。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "徽章會標明某個數字是由 NOOP 在裝置上計算，還是從 Whoop 或 Apple Health 匯入。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A baseline-normalized recovery score: your resting heart rate, sleep quality and night-to-night consistency, weighted against your own baseline, with heart-rate variability (rMSSD) leading wherever the strap gives us a clean reading.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ein an der Basislinie normalisierter Erholungswert: deine Ruheherzfrequenz, Schlafqualität und Konsistenz von Nacht zu Nacht, gewichtet gegen deine eigene Basislinie, wobei die Herzfrequenzvariabilität (rMSSD) führt, wo immer der Strap einen sauberen Messwert liefert."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Una puntuación de recuperación normalizada según tu línea base: tu frecuencia cardíaca en reposo, la calidad del sueño y la consistencia noche a noche, ponderadas contra tu propia línea base, con la variabilidad de la frecuencia cardíaca (rMSSD) al frente siempre que la pulsera nos dé una lectura limpia."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un punteggio di recupero normalizzato sulla linea di base: la tua frequenza cardiaca a riposo, la qualità del sonno e la costanza notte dopo notte, ponderate rispetto alla tua linea di base, con la variabilità della frequenza cardiaca (rMSSD) in primo piano ovunque la fascia ci dia una lettura pulita."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "一个按基线归一化的恢复评分：你的静息心率、睡眠质量和逐夜一致性，均相对于你自身的基线加权，只要手环能给出干净的读数，就以心率变异性（rMSSD）为主导。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "一個以基線正規化的恢復分數：你的靜息心率、睡眠品質與每晚的一致性，皆對照你自己的基線加權，只要手環給出乾淨的讀數，就以心率變異性（rMSSD）為主導。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A blend of how long you slept versus your personal need (the biggest factor), how efficiently (asleep versus in bed), how much was restorative (deep + REM sleep), and how consistent your sleep and wake timing is.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Eine Mischung daraus, wie lange du im Verhältnis zu deinem persönlichen Bedarf geschlafen hast (der größte Faktor), wie effizient (schlafend vs. im Bett), wie viel erholsam war (Tiefschlaf + REM) und wie konsistent deine Schlaf- und Aufwachzeiten sind."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Una combinación de cuánto dormiste frente a tu necesidad personal (el factor más importante), con qué eficiencia (dormido frente a en la cama), cuánto fue reparador (sueño profundo + REM), y qué tan consistentes son tus horarios de sueño y despertar."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un mix di quanto hai dormito rispetto al tuo bisogno personale (il fattore più importante), con quale efficienza (addormentato rispetto a letto), quanto è stato rigenerante (sonno profondo + REM) e quanto sono regolari i tuoi orari di sonno e risveglio."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "综合考量：你的睡眠时长相对于个人需求（最大因素）、睡眠效率（入睡时间与在床时间之比）、恢复性睡眠占比（深睡 + REM 睡眠），以及你的入睡和起床时间是否规律。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "綜合考量你的睡眠時長相對於個人需求（最大的因素）、睡眠效率（實際入睡與躺床時間之比）、恢復性睡眠的比例（深睡 + REM 睡眠），以及你入睡與起床時間的一致性。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A bulk markers CSV import (date, marker, value, unit) lands with the file importers in Data Sources, same as nutrition and lifting. For now, add readings one at a time above. Everything you import stays on %@.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ein Massen-CSV-Import für Marker (Datum, Marker, Wert, Einheit) kommt zu den Datei-Importern in „Datenquellen“, wie schon Ernährung und Krafttraining. Füge Messwerte vorerst oben einzeln hinzu. Alles, was du importierst, bleibt auf %@."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Una importación masiva de marcadores por CSV (fecha, marcador, valor, unidad) llegará con los importadores de archivos en Fuentes de datos, igual que nutrición y pesas. Por ahora, añade lecturas de una en una arriba. Todo lo que importes se queda en %@."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un'importazione di marcatori in blocco da CSV (data, marcatore, valore, unità) arriverà con gli importatori di file in Sorgenti dati, come per nutrizione e sollevamento pesi. Per ora, aggiungi le letture una alla volta qui sopra. Tutto ciò che importi resta su %@."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "批量标记 CSV 导入（日期、标记、数值、单位）将随「数据来源」中的文件导入器一起推出，与营养和力量训练相同。目前请在上方逐条添加读数。你导入的一切都留在 %@ 上。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "批量標記 CSV 匯入（日期、標記、數值、單位）將隨「資料來源」中的檔案匯入器一起推出，與營養和力量訓練相同。目前請在上方逐筆新增讀數。你匯入的一切都留在 %@ 上。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A buzz, not a banner": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ein Vibrieren, kein Banner"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Una vibración, no un banner"
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Una vibrazione, non un banner"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "一次震动，而非横幅"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "一次震動，而非橫幅通知"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A calm evening reminder, timed from your wake time and usual sleep need. It's a suggestion, not an alarm.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Eine ruhige Abenderinnerung, abgestimmt auf deine Aufwachzeit und deinen üblichen Schlafbedarf. Ein Vorschlag, kein Wecker."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un recordatorio tranquilo por la tarde, calculado a partir de tu hora de despertar y tu necesidad habitual de sueño. Es una sugerencia, no una alarma."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un promemoria serale tranquillo, calibrato sulla tua ora di risveglio e sul consueto bisogno di sonno. È un suggerimento, non una sveglia."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "一个平静的傍晚提醒，根据你的起床时间和通常的睡眠需求来定时。它是一个建议，而非闹钟。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "一個平靜的傍晚提醒，根據你的起床時間和通常的睡眠需求來定時。它是一個建議，而非鬧鐘。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A calm hour now helps you hit your wake time well-rested.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Eine ruhige Stunde jetzt hilft dir, deine Aufwachzeit ausgeruht zu erreichen."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Una hora tranquila ahora te ayuda a llegar bien descansado a tu hora de despertar."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un'ora tranquilla adesso ti aiuta ad arrivare riposato alla tua ora di risveglio."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "现在安静一小时，有助于你在起床时间精力充沛地醒来。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "現在安靜地度過一小時，有助於你在起床時間醒來時精神飽滿。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A calm nudge %lldh %lldm before your wake time.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ein sanfter Anstoß %1$lldh %2$lldm vor deiner Aufwachzeit."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "new",
            "value": "A calm nudge %1$lldh %2$lldm before your wake time."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un aviso suave %lldh %lldm antes de tu hora de despertar."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un avviso tranquillo %1$lldh %2$lldm prima della tua ora di risveglio."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在你起床时间前 %1$lld 小时 %2$lld 分钟的一次平静提醒。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在你起床時間前 %1$lld 小時 %2$lld 分鐘的一次平靜提醒。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A cardiovascular load in the Banister TRIMP family: time spent in each heart-rate zone, weighted so harder zones count for more, summed into one daily figure.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Eine kardiovaskuläre Last aus der Banister-TRIMP-Familie: Zeit in jeder Herzfrequenzzone, gewichtet, sodass härtere Zonen mehr zählen, aufsummiert zu einer Tageszahl."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Una carga cardiovascular de la familia TRIMP de Banister: tiempo en cada zona de frecuencia cardíaca, ponderado para que las zonas más duras cuenten más, sumado en una sola cifra diaria."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un carico cardiovascolare della famiglia Banister TRIMP: il tempo trascorso in ciascuna zona di frequenza cardiaca, ponderato in modo che le zone più dure contino di più, sommato in un unico dato giornaliero."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "属于 Banister TRIMP 家族的心血管负荷：统计你在各心率区间的时长，区间越高权重越大，汇总为一个每日数字。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "屬於 Banister TRIMP 家族的心血管負荷：在各心率區間停留的時間，較高強度區間權重更大，加總成每日一個數字。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A clean, shareable one-page PDF of your recovery, sleep, HRV, resting heart rate and strain over a date range. Saved on your %@. Nothing leaves the device.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ein sauberes, teilbares einseitiges PDF deiner Erholung, deines Schlafs, deiner HRV, Ruheherzfrequenz und Belastung über einen Zeitraum. Gespeichert auf deinem %@. Nichts verlässt das Gerät."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un PDF limpio y compartible de una página con tu recuperación, sueño, VFC, frecuencia cardíaca en reposo y esfuerzo en un rango de fechas. Guardado en tu %@. Nada sale del dispositivo."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un PDF di una pagina, ordinato e condivisibile, del tuo recupero, sonno, HRV, frequenza cardiaca a riposo e carico in un intervallo di date. Salvato sul tuo %@, niente lascia il dispositivo."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "一份简洁、可分享的单页 PDF，涵盖某个日期范围内你的恢复、睡眠、HRV、静息心率和强度。保存在你的 %@ 上，没有任何内容离开设备。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "一份簡潔、可分享的單頁 PDF，涵蓋某個日期範圍內你的恢復、睡眠、HRV、靜息心率和強度。保存在你的 %@ 上，沒有任何內容離開裝置。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A couple of metrics depend on which Apple Watch you wear. Wrist temperature, which feeds skin temp, arrived with Series 8, so older watches don't report it. Blood oxygen is the bigger one: Apple removed the SpO₂ sensor from the newest US units over a patent dispute, so those simply don't measure it.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ein paar Metriken hängen davon ab, welche Apple Watch du trägst. Die Handgelenktemperatur, die in die Hauttemperatur einfließt, kam mit der Series 8, ältere Uhren melden sie also nicht. Blutsauerstoff ist der größere Punkt: Apple hat den SpO₂-Sensor wegen eines Patentstreits aus den neuesten US-Geräten entfernt, diese messen ihn also schlicht nicht."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un par de métricas dependen de qué Apple Watch llevas. La temperatura de muñeca, que alimenta la temperatura cutánea, llegó con la Series 8, así que los relojes más antiguos no la reportan. El oxígeno en sangre es la más importante: Apple retiró el sensor de SpO₂ de las unidades más recientes de EE. UU. por una disputa de patentes, así que esas simplemente no lo miden."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un paio di metriche dipendono da quale Apple Watch indossi. La temperatura del polso, che alimenta la temperatura cutanea, è arrivata con la Series 8, quindi i modelli più vecchi non la rilevano. L'ossigeno nel sangue è il caso più rilevante: Apple ha rimosso il sensore SpO₂ dalle unità statunitensi più recenti per una controversia sui brevetti, quindi quelle semplicemente non lo misurano."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "有几项指标取决于你佩戴的 Apple Watch 型号。为皮肤温度提供数据的手腕温度自 Series 8 起才出现，因此更旧的手表不会报告它。血氧影响更大：由于一项专利纠纷，Apple 从最新的美国版机型中移除了 SpO₂ 传感器，所以那些机型根本无法测量它。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "有幾項指標取決於你佩戴的 Apple Watch 型號。為皮膚溫度提供數據的手腕溫度自 Series 8 起才出現，因此更舊的手錶不會報告它。血氧影響更大：由於一項專利糾紛，Apple 從最新的美國版機型中移除了 SpO₂ 感測器，所以那些機型根本無法測量它。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A couple of metrics depend on your model": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ein paar Metriken hängen von deinem Modell ab"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un par de métricas dependen de tu modelo"
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un paio di metriche dipendono dal tuo modello"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "有几项指标取决于你的型号"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "有幾項指標取決於你的型號"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A few honest words, so nothing's a surprise.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ein paar ehrliche Worte, damit nichts überrascht."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Unas palabras honestas, para que nada te sorprenda."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Qualche parola sincera, così niente ti coglie di sorpresa."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "几句实话，免得让你意外。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "先坦白說幾句，免得之後有意外。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A few more days and we can show your Fitness Age.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Noch ein paar Tage, dann können wir dein Fitnessalter zeigen."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Unos días más y podremos mostrar tu Edad fitness."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ancora qualche giorno e potremo mostrarti la tua Età di forma fisica."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "再过几天，我们就能显示你的体能年龄。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "再過幾天，我們就能顯示你的體能年齡。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A few more days and we can show your Vitality.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Noch ein paar Tage, dann können wir deine Vitalität zeigen."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Unos días más y podremos mostrar tu Vitalidad."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ancora qualche giorno e potremo mostrarti la tua Vitalità."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "再过几天，我们就能显示你的活力。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "再過幾天，我們就能顯示你的活力。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A few more days of wear, plus the basics below, and we can show your Fitness Age.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Noch ein paar Tage Tragen plus die Grundangaben unten, dann können wir dein Fitnessalter zeigen."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Unos días más de uso, junto con los datos básicos de abajo, y podremos mostrar tu Edad fitness."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ancora qualche giorno di utilizzo, più le basi qui sotto, e potremo mostrarti la tua Età di forma fisica."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "再佩戴几天，加上下面的基础信息，我们就能显示你的体能年龄。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "再佩戴幾天，加上下面的基礎資訊，我們就能顯示你的體能年齡。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A few signals are up": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ein paar Signale sind erhöht"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Algunas señales están elevadas"
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Alcuni segnali sono in aumento"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "有几项信号偏高"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "有幾項訊號偏高"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A gentle buzz when your HRV drops while your heart rate is calm, a cue to take a paced breath. Rate-limited to once every 15 minutes; off by default.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ein sanftes Vibrieren, wenn deine HRV fällt, während deine Herzfrequenz ruhig ist – ein Anstoß für einen getakteten Atemzug. Auf einmal alle 15 Minuten begrenzt; standardmäßig aus."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Una vibración suave cuando tu VFC baja mientras tu frecuencia cardíaca está tranquila, una señal para respirar con calma. Limitada a una vez cada 15 minutos; desactivada por defecto."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Una vibrazione leggera quando la tua HRV scende mentre la frequenza cardiaca è calma, un invito a fare un respiro ritmato. Limitata a una volta ogni 15 minuti; disattivata per impostazione predefinita."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "当你的 HRV 下降而心率平稳时，轻轻震动一下，提示你做一次有节奏的呼吸。每 15 分钟最多一次；默认关闭。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "當你的 HRV 下降而心率平穩時，給你一次輕柔的震動，提示你做一次節奏呼吸。每 15 分鐘最多一次；預設關閉。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A gentle wrist buzz when you've been sitting too long, a nudge to get up and move. Inferred from the strap's motion on each history sync, so it lags real time by a sync or two.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ein sanftes Vibrieren am Handgelenk, wenn du zu lange gesessen hast – ein Anstoß, aufzustehen und dich zu bewegen. Aus der Bewegung des Straps bei jeder Verlaufssynchronisierung abgeleitet, hinkt es der Echtzeit also ein bis zwei Syncs hinterher."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Una vibración suave en la muñeca cuando llevas demasiado tiempo sentado, un empujón para levantarte y moverte. Se infiere del movimiento de la pulsera en cada sincronización del historial, así que va una o dos sincronizaciones por detrás del tiempo real."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Una vibrazione leggera al polso quando sei seduto da troppo tempo, uno stimolo ad alzarti e muoverti. Dedotta dal movimento della fascia a ogni sincronizzazione della cronologia, quindi è in ritardo di una o due sincronizzazioni rispetto al tempo reale."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "久坐太久时手腕轻轻一震，提醒你起来动一动。它根据每次历史同步时手环的运动数据推断，因此会比实时晚一到两次同步。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "久坐太久時手腕會輕輕震動一下，提醒你起身活動。這是從每次歷史同步時手環的動作推斷的，所以會比即時慢一到兩次同步。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A logged caffeine is past your bedtime cutoff. It may still be on board and keep you up. Just a timing heads-up.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Eine erfasste Koffein-Einnahme liegt nach deiner Schlafenszeit-Grenze. Sie kann noch wirken und dich wachhalten. Nur ein Hinweis zum Timing."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Una cafeína registrada supera tu límite antes de dormir. Puede que siga activa y te mantenga despierto. Solo un aviso de horario."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Una caffeina registrata è oltre il tuo limite serale. Potrebbe essere ancora in circolo e tenerti sveglio. Solo un avviso sui tempi."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "有一条咖啡因记录超过了你的就寝截止时间。它可能仍在起效并让你睡不着。只是一个时间上的提醒。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "一筆記錄的咖啡因已超過你的就寢截止時間。它可能還在體內作用，讓你睡不著。只是提醒一下時間點。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A lower resting heart rate usually means a higher charge.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Eine niedrigere Ruheherzfrequenz bedeutet meist eine höhere Erholung."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Una frecuencia cardíaca en reposo más baja suele significar una carga más alta."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Una frequenza cardiaca a riposo più bassa di solito significa una carica più alta."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "静息心率越低，能量通常越高。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "靜息心率越低，通常能量越高。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A note on blood oxygen and your model": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ein Hinweis zu Blutsauerstoff und deinem Modell"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Una nota sobre el oxígeno en sangre y tu modelo"
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Una nota sull'ossigeno nel sangue e sul tuo modello"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "关于血氧和你的机型的说明"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "關於血氧和你的機型的說明"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A period is likely between %@ and %@ (a window, not a fixed date).": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Eine Periode ist wahrscheinlich zwischen %1$@ und %2$@ (ein Zeitfenster, kein festes Datum)."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "new",
            "value": "A period is likely between %1$@ and %2$@, a window, not a fixed date."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Es probable que la menstruación llegue entre %@ y %@ (una ventana, no una fecha fija)."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un ciclo è probabile tra il %1$@ e il %2$@, una finestra, non una data fissa."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "经期很可能在 %1$@ 到 %2$@ 之间，这是一个时间窗口，而非固定日期。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "經期很可能在 %1$@ 到 %2$@ 之間，這是一個時間窗口，而非固定日期。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A private notebook, not a medical service.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ein privates Notizbuch, kein medizinischer Dienst."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un cuaderno privado, no un servicio médico."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un taccuino privato, non un servizio medico."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "一个私密的笔记本，而非医疗服务。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "一個私密的筆記本，而非醫療服務。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A private window into your recovery, sleep and strain, read straight from your strap, kept only on this Mac.": {
      "extractionState": "stale",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ein privater Blick auf deine Erholung, deinen Schlaf und deine Belastung, direkt vom Strap gelesen und nur auf diesem Mac gespeichert."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "A private window into your recovery, sleep and strain, read straight from your strap, kept only on this Mac."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Una ventana privada a tu recuperación, sueño y esfuerzo, leída directamente desde tu pulsera y guardada solo en esta Mac."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Une fenêtre privée sur votre récupération, sommeil et strain, lu directement depuis votre bracelet, conservé uniquement sur ce Mac."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Una finestra privata sul tuo recupero, sonno e carico, letti direttamente dalla tua fascia, conservati solo su questo Mac."
          }
        },
        "ru": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Личное окно с вашими показателями восстановления, сна и нагрузки, данные поступают напрямую с браслета и хранятся только на этом Mac"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "一扇通往你恢复、睡眠与强度的私密窗口，，直接从手环读取，只保存在这台 Mac 上。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "一扇通往你恢復、睡眠與強度的私密窗口，，直接從手環讀取，只保存在這台 Mac 上。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A private window into your recovery, sleep and strain. Read straight from your strap, kept only on %@.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ein privater Blick auf deine Erholung, deinen Schlaf und deine Belastung. Direkt vom Strap gelesen, nur auf %@ gespeichert."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Una ventana privada a tu recuperación, sueño y esfuerzo. Leída directamente desde tu pulsera y guardada solo en %@."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Una finestra privata sul tuo recupero, sonno e carico, letta direttamente dalla tua fascia, conservata solo su %@."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "一扇通往你恢复、睡眠与强度的私密窗口，直接从手环读取，只保存在 %@ 上。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "一扇通往你恢復、睡眠與強度的私密窗口，直接從手環讀取，只保存在 %@ 上。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A quick word before we connect": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ein kurzes Wort, bevor wir verbinden"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Unas palabras rápidas antes de conectar"
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Due parole prima di connetterci"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "连接之前先说几句"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "連線前先說幾句"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A read-only export of the decoded sensor streams NOOP already stores. Works on any strap. Nothing is written to your device, and nothing is uploaded.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ein schreibgeschützter Export der dekodierten Sensor-Streams, die NOOP bereits speichert. Funktioniert mit jedem Strap. Nichts wird auf dein Gerät geschrieben, nichts hochgeladen."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Una exportación de solo lectura de los flujos de sensores decodificados que NOOP ya almacena. Funciona con cualquier pulsera. No se escribe nada en tu dispositivo y no se sube nada."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un'esportazione in sola lettura degli stream dei sensori decodificati che NOOP già memorizza. Funziona con qualsiasi fascia, niente viene scritto sul tuo dispositivo e niente viene caricato."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "对 NOOP 已存储的已解码传感器数据流进行只读导出。适用于任何手环，不会向你的设备写入任何内容，也不会上传任何内容。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "對 NOOP 已儲存的已解碼感測器資料流進行唯讀匯出。適用於任何手環，不會向你的裝置寫入任何內容，也不會上傳任何內容。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A relaxation rhythm, not cardiac control. It never paces below a safe rate and you can stop anytime. If your heart rate doesn't settle, we'll say so plainly.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ein Entspannungsrhythmus, keine Herzsteuerung. Er taktet nie unter eine sichere Rate, und du kannst jederzeit aufhören. Wenn sich deine Herzfrequenz nicht beruhigt, sagen wir es klar."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un ritmo de relajación, no un control cardíaco. Nunca marca un ritmo por debajo de un nivel seguro y puedes parar cuando quieras. Si tu frecuencia cardíaca no se calma, te lo diremos claramente."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un ritmo di rilassamento, non un controllo cardiaco. Non scende mai sotto una frequenza sicura e puoi fermarti in qualsiasi momento. Se la tua frequenza cardiaca non si stabilizza, te lo diremo chiaramente."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "一种放松的节律，而非对心脏的控制。它绝不会将节奏降到安全心率以下，你可以随时停止。如果你的心率没有平复，我们会如实告知。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "一種放鬆的節律，而非對心臟的控制。它絕不會將節奏降到安全心率以下，你可以隨時停止。如果你的心率沒有平復，我們會如實告知。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A reminder to recharge before bed when the strap drops to 15%, and a heads-up when it reaches 100%, each at most once per charge cycle.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Eine Erinnerung, vor dem Schlafengehen zu laden, wenn der Strap auf 15 % fällt, und ein Hinweis, wenn er 100 % erreicht – jeweils höchstens einmal pro Ladezyklus."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un recordatorio para recargar antes de dormir cuando la pulsera baja al 15%, y un aviso cuando llega al 100%, cada uno como máximo una vez por ciclo de carga."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un promemoria per ricaricare prima di dormire quando la fascia scende al 15% e un avviso quando raggiunge il 100%, ciascuno al massimo una volta per ciclo di carica."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "手环电量降到 15% 时提醒你睡前充电，充到 100% 时再提醒一次，每个充电周期各最多一次。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "手環電量降到 15% 時提醒你睡前充電，充到 100% 時通知你，每個充電週期各最多一次。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A ring talks to one owner at a time.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ein Ring spricht immer nur mit einem Besitzer."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un anillo habla con un solo dueño a la vez."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un anello comunica con un solo proprietario alla volta."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "戒指一次只能与一个持有者通信。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "戒指一次只能與一個持有者通信。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A shareable one-page PDF of recovery, sleep, HRV, resting HR and strain over a range, saved on your %@.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ein teilbares einseitiges PDF von Erholung, Schlaf, HRV, Ruheherzfrequenz und Belastung über einen Zeitraum, gespeichert auf deinem %@."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un PDF compartible de una página con recuperación, sueño, VFC, FC en reposo y esfuerzo en un rango, guardado en tu %@."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un PDF di una pagina condivisibile di recupero, sonno, HRV, FC a riposo e carico in un intervallo, salvato sul tuo %@."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "一份可分享的单页 PDF，涵盖某个范围内的恢复、睡眠、HRV、静息心率和强度，保存在你的 %@ 上。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "一份可分享的單頁 PDF，涵蓋某個範圍內的恢復、睡眠、HRV、靜息心率和強度，保存在你的 %@ 上。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A signature ring distils HRV, resting heart rate and sleep into one calm read on whether to push or rest.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ein Signatur-Ring verdichtet HRV, Ruheherzfrequenz und Schlaf zu einer ruhigen Aussage, ob du Gas geben oder ruhen solltest."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un anillo distintivo que resume la VFC, la frecuencia cardíaca en reposo y el sueño en una lectura serena sobre si exigirte o descansar."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un anello distintivo che condensa HRV, frequenza cardiaca a riposo e sonno in un'unica lettura tranquilla su quando spingere o riposare."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "一枚标志性圆环将 HRV、静息心率和睡眠浓缩为一个平静的判断：该冲还是该歇。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "一個標誌性的圓環，將 HRV、靜息心率與睡眠濃縮成一個平靜的判讀：該衝還是該休息。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A simple goal that adjusts to your effort. General wellness guidance, not medical advice.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ein einfaches Ziel, das sich deiner Belastung anpasst. Allgemeine Wellness-Orientierung, kein medizinischer Rat."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Una meta simple que se ajusta a tu esfuerzo. Orientación general de bienestar, no consejo médico."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un obiettivo semplice che si adatta al tuo sforzo. Indicazioni generali di benessere, non consigli medici."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "一个会根据你的消耗进行调整的简单目标。一般性的健康指引，而非医疗建议。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "一個會根據你的消耗進行調整的簡單目標。一般性的健康指引，而非醫療建議。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A standalone companion for your WHOOP. Everything stays on this device, your history, your live stream, your numbers. Nothing is uploaded. NOOP is an independent, experimental project, not the WHOOP app.": {
      "extractionState": "stale",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ein eigenständiger Begleiter für dein WHOOP. Alles bleibt auf diesem Gerät, deine Historie, dein Live-Stream, deine Werte. Nichts wird hochgeladen. NOOP ist ein unabhängiges, experimentelles Projekt, nicht die WHOOP-App."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "A standalone companion for your WHOOP. Everything stays on this device, your history, your live stream, your numbers. Nothing is uploaded. NOOP is an independent, experimental project, not the WHOOP app."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un complemento independiente para tu WHOOP. Todo permanece en este dispositivo: tu historial, tu transmisión de datos, tus números. No se sube nada. NOOP es un proyecto independiente y experimental, no la app de WHOOP."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un compagnon autonome pour votre WHOOP. Tout reste sur cet appareil, votre historique, votre flux en direct, vos chiffres. Rien n'est téléchargé. NOOP est un projet indépendant et expérimental, pas l'application WHOOP."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un'app companion autonoma per il tuo WHOOP. Tutto resta su questo dispositivo, la tua cronologia, il tuo flusso in diretta, i tuoi numeri. Nulla viene caricato online. NOOP è un progetto indipendente e sperimentale, non è l'app WHOOP."
          }
        },
        "ru": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Это отдельное приложение-компаньон для вашего браслета Whoop. Все данные, история, поток измерений в реальном времени, показатели, хранятся только на этом устройстве, ничего не отправляется в облако. NOOP, независимый экспериментальный проект, и это не официальное приложение Whoop."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "为你的 WHOOP 打造的独立伴侣应用。一切都留在这台设备上，，你的历史、你的实时数据流、你的各项数值。不上传任何内容。NOOP 是一个独立的实验性项目，并非 WHOOP 官方应用。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "為你的 WHOOP 打造的獨立伴侶應用程式。一切都留在這台裝置上，，你的歷史、你的即時資料流、你的各項數值。不上傳任何內容。NOOP 是一個獨立的實驗性專案，並非 WHOOP 官方應用程式。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A standalone companion for your WHOOP. Everything stays on this device: your history, your live stream, your numbers. Nothing is uploaded. NOOP is an independent, experimental project, not the WHOOP app.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ein eigenständiger Begleiter für dein WHOOP. Alles bleibt auf diesem Gerät: dein Verlauf, dein Live-Stream, deine Zahlen. Nichts wird hochgeladen. NOOP ist ein unabhängiges, experimentelles Projekt, nicht die WHOOP-App."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un complemento independiente para tu WHOOP. Todo permanece en este dispositivo: tu historial, tu transmisión en vivo, tus números. No se sube nada. NOOP es un proyecto independiente y experimental, no la app de WHOOP."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un compagno autonomo per il tuo WHOOP. Tutto resta su questo dispositivo, la tua cronologia, il tuo stream in diretta, i tuoi numeri. Niente viene caricato. NOOP è un progetto indipendente e sperimentale, non l'app WHOOP."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "为你的 WHOOP 打造的独立伴侣应用。一切都留在这台设备上，你的历史、你的实时数据流、你的各项数值。不上传任何内容。NOOP 是一个独立的实验性项目，并非 WHOOP 官方应用。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "為你的 WHOOP 打造的獨立伴侶應用程式。一切都留在這台裝置上，你的歷史、你的即時資料流、你的各項數值。不上傳任何內容。NOOP 是一個獨立的實驗性專案，並非 WHOOP 官方應用程式。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A still, seated snapshot of your heart-rate variability": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Eine ruhige Momentaufnahme deiner Herzfrequenzvariabilität im Sitzen"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Una instantánea de tu variabilidad de frecuencia cardíaca, sentado y en reposo"
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un'istantanea da fermo, da seduto, della tua variabilità della frequenza cardiaca"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在静坐状态下对你心率变异性的一次快照"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在靜坐狀態下對你心率變異性的一次快照"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A sync is already in progress.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Eine Synchronisierung läuft bereits."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ya hay una sincronización en curso."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Una sincronizzazione è già in corso."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "同步已在进行中。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "同步已在進行中。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A transparent cardiorespiratory recipe that recovers deep and REM better than the default staging. Opt-in and experimental: it only changes how already-detected nights are split into stages (detection and scores are unchanged), and the default staging stays in place if you leave this off. Takes effect on the next nights staged.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ein transparentes kardiorespiratorisches Rezept, das Tiefschlaf und REM besser rekonstruiert als die Standard-Phaseneinteilung. Opt-in und experimentell: Es ändert nur, wie bereits erkannte Nächte in Phasen aufgeteilt werden (Erkennung und Werte bleiben unverändert), und die Standard-Einteilung bleibt bestehen, wenn du es aus lässt. Wirkt ab den nächsten eingeteilten Nächten."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Una receta cardiorrespiratoria transparente que recupera el sueño profundo y REM mejor que la clasificación por defecto. Opcional y experimental: solo cambia cómo se dividen en fases las noches ya detectadas (la detección y las puntuaciones no cambian), y la clasificación por defecto se mantiene si lo dejas desactivado. Se aplica a las próximas noches clasificadas."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Una ricetta cardiorespiratoria trasparente che recupera meglio il sonno profondo e REM rispetto allo staging predefinito. Facoltativa e sperimentale, cambia solo come le notti già rilevate vengono divise in fasi (rilevamento e punteggi restano invariati), e lo staging predefinito resta attivo se la lasci disattivata. Ha effetto sulle prossime notti elaborate."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "一套透明的心肺算法，比默认的分期能更好地还原深睡和 REM。需主动开启且为实验性，它只改变已检测到的夜晚如何被划分为各阶段（检测和评分不变），如果你保持关闭，则沿用默认分期。将在下次分期的夜晚生效。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "一套透明的心肺演算法，比預設的分期能更好地還原深睡和 REM。需主動開啟且為實驗性，它只改變已偵測到的夜晚如何被劃分為各階段（偵測和評分不變），如果你保持關閉，則沿用預設分期。將在下次分期的夜晚生效。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A typical recent day": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ein typischer Tag der letzten Zeit"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un día reciente típico"
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Una giornata recente tipica"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "近期的典型一天"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "近期的一個典型日子"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A watch samples your heart-rate variability rather than streaming it all night, so your Charge score needs roughly seven nights to calibrate. Until then NOOP shows “needs more data”, never a guessed number.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Eine Uhr misst deine Herzfrequenzvariabilität stichprobenartig, statt sie die ganze Nacht zu streamen, daher braucht dein Ladungswert etwa sieben Nächte zum Kalibrieren. Bis dahin zeigt NOOP „braucht mehr Daten“, nie eine geratene Zahl."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un reloj toma muestras de tu variabilidad de frecuencia cardíaca en lugar de transmitirla toda la noche, así que tu puntuación de Carga necesita unas siete noches para calibrarse. Hasta entonces, NOOP muestra “necesita más datos”, nunca un número inventado."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un orologio campiona la tua variabilità della frequenza cardiaca invece di trasmetterla tutta la notte, quindi il tuo punteggio di carica ha bisogno di circa sette notti per calibrarsi. Fino ad allora NOOP mostra “servono più dati”, mai un numero indovinato."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "手表只是对心率变异性进行采样，而不是整晚持续串流，所以你的能量评分大约需要七晚来校准。在那之前 NOOP 会显示「需要更多数据」，绝不给出猜测的数字。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "手錶是對你的心率變異性抽樣，而非整夜串流，所以你的能量分數大約需要七個晚上來校準。在那之前 NOOP 會顯示「需要更多資料」，絕不顯示猜測的數字。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A weekly digest needs a few days of history. Wear your strap or import your WHOOP export in Data Sources.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Eine Wochenübersicht braucht ein paar Tage Verlauf. Trage deinen Strap oder importiere deinen WHOOP-Export unter „Datenquellen“."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un resumen semanal necesita unos días de historial. Usa tu pulsera o importa tu exportación de WHOOP en Fuentes de datos."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un riepilogo settimanale richiede qualche giorno di cronologia. Indossa la tua fascia o importa la tua esportazione WHOOP in Sorgenti dati."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "每周摘要需要几天的历史数据。请佩戴你的手环，或在「数据来源」中导入你的 WHOOP 导出文件。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "每週摘要需要幾天的歷史資料。請佩戴你的手環，或在「資料來源」中匯入你的 WHOOP 匯出檔案。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A wellness estimate from your habits, not a clinical biological age.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Eine Wellness-Schätzung aus deinen Gewohnheiten, kein klinisches biologisches Alter."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Una estimación de bienestar a partir de tus hábitos, no una edad biológica clínica."
          }
        },
