    "An HRV reading needs the live R-R stream. Open the Live screen and connect your strap, then come back.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Eine HRV-Messung braucht den Live-R-R-Stream. Öffne den Live-Bildschirm und verbinde deinen Strap, dann komm zurück."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Una lectura de VFC necesita el flujo R-R en vivo. Abre la pantalla En vivo y conecta tu pulsera, luego vuelve."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Una lettura HRV richiede lo stream R-R in diretta. Apri la schermata In diretta e connetti la tua fascia, poi torna qui."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "HRV 读数需要实时 R-R 数据流。请打开「实时」界面并连接你的手环，然后再返回。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "HRV 讀數需要即時 R-R 資料流。請打開「即時」畫面並連接你的手環，然後再返回。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "An estimated VO2max from the Nes / HUNT Fitness Study model (resting heart rate, age and activity), read against population norms to express it as a fitness age.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Eine geschätzte VO2max nach dem Modell der Nes-/HUNT-Fitness-Studie (Ruheherzfrequenz, Alter und Aktivität), gegen Bevölkerungsnormen gelesen, um sie als Fitnessalter auszudrücken."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un VO2max estimado con el modelo del estudio Nes / HUNT Fitness (frecuencia cardíaca en reposo, edad y actividad), comparado con normas poblacionales para expresarlo como una edad fitness."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un VO2max stimato con il modello del Nes / HUNT Fitness Study (frequenza cardiaca a riposo, età e attività), confrontato con le norme di popolazione per esprimerlo come età fitness."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "基于 Nes / HUNT 健身研究模型估算的 VO2max（静息心率、年龄和活动量），对照人群常模换算为体能年龄。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "依 Nes / HUNT Fitness Study 模型估算的 VO2max（靜息心率、年齡與活動量），對照人口常模換算成體能年齡。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "An experimental picture of your beat-to-beat heart timing. Not an ECG and not a diagnosis. You'll read and accept an experimental note before it shows anything.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ein experimentelles Bild deines Herzschlag-Timings. Kein EKG und keine Diagnose. Du liest und akzeptierst einen Experimentell-Hinweis, bevor es etwas anzeigt."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Una imagen experimental del intervalo entre tus latidos. No es un ECG ni un diagnóstico. Leerás y aceptarás una nota experimental antes de que muestre nada."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un quadro sperimentale del ritmo battito per battito del tuo cuore. Non è un ECG e non è una diagnosi. Leggerai e accetterai una nota sperimentale prima che mostri qualcosa."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "一幅实验性的逐拍心跳节律图。它不是心电图，也不是诊断。在显示任何内容之前，你需要先阅读并接受一份实验性说明。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "一幅你逐拍心跳間隔的實驗性圖像。不是 ECG，也不是診斷。在它顯示任何內容之前，你需要先閱讀並接受一份實驗性說明。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "An experimental picture of your beat-to-beat timing": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ein experimentelles Bild deines Herzschlag-Timings"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Una imagen experimental del intervalo entre tus latidos"
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un quadro sperimentale della tua tempistica battito-battito"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "对你逐拍节律的一次实验性呈现"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "對你逐拍節律的一次實驗性呈現"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "An experimental picture of your beat-to-beat timing. Please read these first.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ein experimentelles Bild deines Herzschlag-Timings. Bitte lies das zuerst."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Una imagen experimental del intervalo entre tus latidos. Lee esto primero, por favor."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Un quadro sperimentale della tua tempistica battito-battito. Leggi prima questo."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "对你逐拍节律的一次实验性呈现。请先阅读以下内容。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "對你逐拍節律的一次實驗性呈現。請先閱讀以下內容。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Analyse my sleep": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Meinen Schlaf analysieren"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Analizar mi sueño"
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Analizza il mio sonno"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "分析我的睡眠"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "分析我的睡眠"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "And make sure it's charged.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Und stelle sicher, dass er geladen ist."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Y asegúrate de que esté cargada."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "E assicurati che sia carica."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "并确保它已充好电。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "還要確保它有電。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Answers are about the night and day leading into this morning, the same attribution a WHOOP export uses, so logged and imported days line up.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Antworten beziehen sich auf die Nacht und den Tag vor diesem Morgen, dieselbe Zuordnung wie in einem WHOOP-Export, damit erfasste und importierte Tage übereinstimmen."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Las respuestas se refieren a la noche y el día previos a esta mañana, la misma atribución que usa una exportación de WHOOP, para que los días registrados e importados coincidan."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Le risposte riguardano la notte e il giorno che portano a questa mattina, la stessa attribuzione usata da un'esportazione WHOOP, così i giorni registrati e importati si allineano."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "回答涉及的是通向今天早晨的这个夜晚和白天，与 WHOOP 导出所用的归属方式相同，因此记录的日期和导入的日期能够对齐。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "回答涉及的是通向今天早晨的這個夜晚和白天，與 WHOOP 匯出所用的歸屬方式相同，因此記錄的日期和匯入的日期能夠對齊。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Any OpenAI-compatible server: Ollama, LM Studio, llama.cpp, or your own gateway. Stays on your network; nothing leaves %@.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Jeder OpenAI-kompatible Server: Ollama, LM Studio, llama.cpp oder dein eigenes Gateway. Bleibt in deinem Netzwerk; nichts verlässt %@."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Cualquier servidor compatible con OpenAI: Ollama, LM Studio, llama.cpp o tu propia pasarela. Se queda en tu red; nada sale de %@."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Qualsiasi server compatibile con OpenAI, Ollama, LM Studio, llama.cpp o il tuo gateway. Resta sulla tua rete; niente lascia %@."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "任何兼容 OpenAI 的服务器，Ollama、LM Studio、llama.cpp，或你自己的网关。留在你的网络内；没有任何内容离开 %@。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "任何相容 OpenAI 的伺服器，Ollama、LM Studio、llama.cpp，或你自己的閘道。留在你的網路內；沒有任何內容離開 %@。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Any amount helps. Thank you, genuinely.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Jeder Betrag hilft. Danke, wirklich."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Any amount helps. Thank you, genuinely."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Cualquier cantidad ayuda. Gracias, de verdad."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tout montant est utile. Merci, sincèrement."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Qualsiasi importo aiuta. Grazie, davvero."
          }
        },
        "ru": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Любая сумма поможет. Спасибо, искренне."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "任何金额都有帮助。谢谢你，真心的。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "任何金額都有幫助。謝謝你，真心的。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Anything that needs Oura's cloud (web dashboard, Oura's coaching, shared circles).": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Alles, was Ouras Cloud braucht (Web-Dashboard, Ouras Coaching, geteilte Kreise)."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Todo lo que necesite la nube de Oura (panel web, coaching de Oura, círculos compartidos)."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tutto ciò che richiede il cloud di Oura (dashboard web, coaching di Oura, cerchie condivise)."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "任何依赖 Oura 云端的功能（网页仪表盘、Oura 的教练服务、共享圈子）。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "任何需要 Oura 雲端的功能（網頁儀表板、Oura 的教練功能、共享圈子）。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Anything you see here (including any side-by-side trend) is your own information shown back to you. It's an association, never a cause, and never a medical finding.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Alles, was du hier siehst (einschließlich Seite-an-Seite-Trends), sind deine eigenen Informationen, die dir zurückgespiegelt werden. Es ist ein Zusammenhang, nie eine Ursache und nie ein medizinischer Befund."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Todo lo que ves aquí (incluida cualquier tendencia comparada) es tu propia información mostrada de vuelta. Es una asociación, nunca una causa, y nunca un hallazgo médico."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tutto quello che vedi qui (compresa qualsiasi tendenza affiancata) sono le tue informazioni mostrate a te. È un'associazione, mai una causa, e mai un riscontro medico."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "你在这里看到的一切（包括任何并排趋势）都只是把你自己的信息呈现给你。它是一种关联，绝不是因果，更不是医学结论。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "你在這裡看到的一切（包括任何並排趨勢）都是你自己的資訊回饋給你。它是一種關聯，絕非因果，也絕非醫學結論。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
