            "state": "translated",
            "value": "4月"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Armed on the strap itself, so it can buzz at your wake time even if your phone is asleep or NOOP is closed. We send the same alarm command the official app sends, but a strap-driven wake-up hasn't been confirmed on our side yet, so please keep a backup alarm for now.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Auf dem Strap selbst scharfgestellt, er kann also zu deiner Aufwachzeit vibrieren, selbst wenn dein Telefon schläft oder NOOP geschlossen ist. Wir senden denselben Weckbefehl wie die offizielle App, aber ein Strap-gesteuertes Wecken ist unsererseits noch nicht bestätigt – halte also vorerst bitte einen Ersatzwecker bereit."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Se activa en la propia pulsera, así que puede vibrar a tu hora de despertar aunque tu teléfono esté en reposo o NOOP esté cerrado. Enviamos el mismo comando de alarma que envía la app oficial, pero aún no hemos confirmado por nuestra parte un despertar activado por la pulsera, así que mantén una alarma de respaldo por ahora."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Impostata sulla fascia stessa, così può vibrare all'ora del risveglio anche se il telefono è in standby o NOOP è chiuso. Inviamo lo stesso comando di sveglia dell'app ufficiale, ma un risveglio gestito dalla fascia non è ancora stato confermato da parte nostra, quindi per ora tieni una sveglia di riserva."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在手环本身上设定，因此即使你的手机处于睡眠状态或 NOOP 已关闭，它也能在你的起床时间震动。我们发送的是与官方应用相同的闹钟指令，但由手环驱动的唤醒尚未在我们这边得到确认，因此目前请保留一个备用闹钟。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在手環本身上設定，因此即使你的手機處於睡眠狀態或 NOOP 已關閉，它也能在你的起床時間震動。我們發送的是與官方應用程式相同的鬧鐘指令，但由手環驅動的喚醒尚未在我們這邊得到確認，因此目前請保留一個備用鬧鐘。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Arms the strap to buzz at your wake time, even if NOOP is closed. Still experimental on WHOOP 4.0, so keep a backup alarm until you've confirmed it wakes you.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Stellt den Strap scharf, damit er zu deiner Aufwachzeit vibriert, selbst wenn NOOP geschlossen ist. Auf WHOOP 4.0 noch experimentell, also halte einen Ersatzwecker bereit, bis du bestätigt hast, dass es dich weckt."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Programa la pulsera para vibrar a tu hora de despertar, aunque NOOP esté cerrado. Aún es experimental en WHOOP 4.0, así que mantén una alarma de respaldo hasta confirmar que te despierta."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Imposta la fascia per vibrare all'ora del risveglio, anche se NOOP è chiuso. È ancora sperimentale su WHOOP 4.0, quindi tieni una sveglia di riserva finché non hai verificato che ti svegli."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "设定手环在你的起床时间震动，即使 NOOP 已关闭。在 WHOOP 4.0 上仍属实验性，因此在你确认它能叫醒你之前，请保留一个备用闹钟。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "設定手環在你的起床時間震動，即使 NOOP 已關閉。在 WHOOP 4.0 上仍屬實驗性，因此在你確認它能叫醒你之前，請保留一個備用鬧鐘。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Ask Coach about your data…": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Frage den Coach zu deinen Daten…"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ask Coach about your data…"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pregunta al Coach sobre tus datos…"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Demandez à Coach à propos de vos données…"
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Chiedi al Coach informazioni sui tuoi dati…"
          }
        },
        "ru": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Спросите ИИ-тренера о ваших данных…"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "向教练询问你的数据…"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "向教練詢問你的數據…"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Ask about your charge, effort, rest and workouts, grounded in your own numbers.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Frage nach deiner Erholung, Belastung, Schlaf und deinen Workouts, basierend auf deinen eigenen Zahlen."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pregunta sobre tu carga, esfuerzo, descanso y entrenamientos, basados en tus propios números."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Chiedi della tua carica, dello sforzo, del riposo e degli allenamenti, basandoti sui tuoi numeri."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "询问你的能量、消耗、休息和锻炼，一切都基于你自己的数据。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "詢問你的能量、消耗、休息和鍛鍊，一切都基於你自己的數據。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Ask about your recovery, strain, sleep and workouts, grounded in your own numbers.": {
      "extractionState": "stale",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Frage nach deiner Erholung, Belastung, deinem Schlaf und deinen Workouts, basierend auf deinen eigenen Werten."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ask about your recovery, strain, sleep and workouts, grounded in your own numbers."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pregunta sobre tu recuperación, esfuerzo, sueño y entrenamientos, basados en tus propios números."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Posez des questions sur votre récupération, strain, sommeil et entraînements, basées sur vos propres chiffres."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Fai domande su recupero, carico, sonno e allenamenti, basate sui tuoi numeri."
          }
        },
        "ru": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Спрашивайте о восстановлении, нагрузке, сне и тренировках, на основе ваших собственных данных."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "询问你的恢复、强度、睡眠和锻炼，，一切都基于你自己的数据。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "詢問你的恢復、強度、睡眠和鍛鍊，，一切都基於你自己的數據。"
          }
        }
