    "Buzz when you hit your top zone (ease off) and again when you recover. Uses your max HR from Settings.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Vibriert, wenn du deine oberste Zone erreichst (runterschalten), und erneut, wenn du dich erholst. Nutzt deine maximale HF aus den Einstellungen."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Vibra cuando llegas a tu zona máxima (afloja) y otra vez cuando te recuperas. Usa tu FC máxima de Ajustes."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Vibra quando raggiungi la tua zona massima (rallenta) e di nuovo quando recuperi. Usa la tua FC massima dalle Impostazioni."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "达到最高心率区间时震动（提示放松），恢复后再次震动。使用「设置」中的最大心率。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "當你進入最高區間時震動（提醒放慢），恢復後再震動一次。使用「設定」中的最大心率。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Buzz your strap or mark a moment from Siri, Spotlight, the Shortcuts app, or a Back-Tap / automation. No setup needed.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Lass deinen Strap vibrieren oder markiere einen Moment über Siri, Spotlight, die Kurzbefehle-App oder ein Back-Tap/eine Automation. Keine Einrichtung nötig."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Haz vibrar tu pulsera o marca un momento desde Siri, Spotlight, la app Atajos o un Back-Tap / automatización. Sin configuración."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Fai vibrare la fascia o registra un momento da Siri, Spotlight, l'app Comandi o un Back-Tap / un'automazione, senza alcuna configurazione."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "通过 Siri、聚焦搜索、快捷指令应用，或轻点背面 / 自动化来震动你的手环或标记某个时刻，无需任何设置。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "透過 Siri、Spotlight、捷徑應用程式，或輕點背面 / 自動化來震動你的手環或標記某個時刻，無需任何設定。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Buzz your strap when these apps notify you. Everything runs on %@.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Lass deinen Strap vibrieren, wenn diese Apps dich benachrichtigen. Alles läuft auf %@."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Haz vibrar tu pulsera cuando estas apps te notifiquen. Todo se ejecuta en %@."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Fai vibrare la fascia quando queste app ti inviano una notifica. Tutto viene eseguito su %@."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "当这些应用通知你时，让手环震动。一切都在 %@ 上运行。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "當這些應用程式通知你時，讓手環震動。一切都在 %@ 上執行。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
