    "Changes the Bluetooth name your WHOOP 4.0 advertises (what you see when pairing). The strap reboots to apply, so the new name appears the next time it connects. WHOOP 4.0 only.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ändert den Bluetooth-Namen, den dein WHOOP 4.0 sendet (was du beim Koppeln siehst). Der Strap startet zum Übernehmen neu, der neue Name erscheint also bei der nächsten Verbindung. Nur WHOOP 4.0."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Cambia el nombre Bluetooth que anuncia tu WHOOP 4.0 (lo que ves al emparejar). La pulsera se reinicia para aplicarlo, así que el nuevo nombre aparece la próxima vez que se conecte. Solo WHOOP 4.0."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Cambia il nome Bluetooth diffuso dal tuo WHOOP 4.0, quello che vedi durante l'associazione. La fascia si riavvia per applicarlo, quindi il nuovo nome appare alla connessione successiva. Solo WHOOP 4.0."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "更改你的 WHOOP 4.0 广播的蓝牙名称，即你配对时看到的名称。手环会重启以应用更改，因此新名称会在它下次连接时出现。仅限 WHOOP 4.0。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "變更你的 WHOOP 4.0 廣播的藍牙名稱，即你配對時看到的名稱。手環會重啟以套用變更，因此新名稱會在它下次連接時出現。僅限 WHOOP 4.0。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
