    "Coach reads a summary of your last two weeks plus 30-day averages and recent workouts, then answers in plain language. Try a suggestion below.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Der Coach liest eine Zusammenfassung deiner letzten zwei Wochen sowie 30-Tage-Durchschnitte und aktuelle Workouts und antwortet dann in klarer Sprache. Probiere einen Vorschlag unten aus."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Coach reads a summary of your last two weeks plus 30-day averages and recent workouts, then answers in plain language. Try a suggestion below."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "El Entrenador lee un resumen de tus últimas dos semanas más los promedios de 30 días y los entrenamientos recientes, y luego responde en lenguaje sencillo. Prueba una sugerencia a continuación."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Coach lit un résumé de vos deux dernières semaines, les moyennes sur 30 jours et vos récents entraînements, puis répond en langage clair. Essayez une suggestion ci-dessous."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Il Coach legge un riepilogo delle tue ultime due settimane più le medie su 30 giorni e gli allenamenti recenti, poi risponde in linguaggio naturale. Prova un suggerimento qui sotto."
          }
        },
        "ru": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ИИ-тренер анализирует сводку за последние две недели, средние показатели за 30 дней и недавние тренировки, а затем отвечает понятным языком. Попробуйте один из вариантов ниже."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "教练会读取你最近两周的摘要，以及 30 天平均值和近期锻炼，然后用通俗的语言作答。试试下面的建议。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "教練會讀取你最近兩週的摘要，以及 30 天平均值和近期鍛鍊，然後用通俗的語言作答。試試下面的建議。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Coach said: %@": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Coach sagte: %@"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Coach said: %@"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "El Entrenador dijo: %@"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Coach a dit : %@"
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Il Coach ha detto: %@"
          }
        },
        "ru": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ИИ-тренер: %@"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "教练说：%@"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "教練說：%@"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Coach talks only to the server URL you set. Point it at a local model (Ollama, LM Studio, llama.cpp) to keep everything on your own machine. Nothing is sent until you ask.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Der Coach spricht nur mit der Server-URL, die du festlegst. Richte ihn auf ein lokales Modell (Ollama, LM Studio, llama.cpp), um alles auf deinem eigenen Rechner zu behalten. Nichts wird gesendet, bis du fragst."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "El coach solo se comunica con la URL del servidor que configures. Apúntalo a un modelo local (Ollama, LM Studio, llama.cpp) para mantener todo en tu propia máquina. No se envía nada hasta que tú lo pidas."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Coach comunica solo con l'URL del server che imposti, puntalo a un modello locale (Ollama, LM Studio, llama.cpp) per mantenere tutto sulla tua macchina. Non viene inviato nulla finché non lo richiedi."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "教练只与你设置的服务器 URL 通信，将它指向一个本地模型（Ollama、LM Studio、llama.cpp），即可让一切都留在你自己的机器上。在你主动请求之前，不会发送任何内容。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "教練只與你設定的伺服器 URL 通信，將它指向一個本地模型（Ollama、LM Studio、llama.cpp），即可讓一切都留在你自己的機器上。在你主動請求之前，不會發送任何內容。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Coach uses your own API key. Pick a provider, paste a key, and choose a model. Your key is stored securely in the Keychain and never leaves %@ except as the request you make.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Der Coach nutzt deinen eigenen API-Schlüssel. Wähle einen Anbieter, füge einen Schlüssel ein und wähle ein Modell. Dein Schlüssel wird sicher im Schlüsselbund gespeichert und verlässt %@ nur als die Anfrage, die du stellst."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "El coach usa tu propia clave de API. Elige un proveedor, pega una clave y selecciona un modelo. Tu clave se guarda de forma segura en el Llavero y nunca sale de %@ salvo en la solicitud que tú haces."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Coach usa la tua chiave API. Scegli un provider, incolla una chiave e seleziona un modello. La tua chiave viene memorizzata in modo sicuro nel Keychain e non lascia mai %@ se non come la richiesta che effettui."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "教练使用你自己的 API 密钥。选择一个服务商，粘贴密钥，再选择一个模型。你的密钥安全地存储在钥匙串中，除了你发起的请求外，绝不会离开 %@。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "教練使用你自己的 API 金鑰。選擇一個服務供應商，貼上金鑰，再選擇一個模型。你的金鑰安全地儲存在鑰匙圈中，除了你發起的請求外，絕不會離開 %@。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Coach uses your own API key. Pick a provider, paste a key, and choose a model. Your key is stored securely in the macOS Keychain and never leaves your Mac except as the request you make.": {
      "extractionState": "stale",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Der Coach nutzt deinen eigenen API-Schlüssel. Wähle einen Anbieter, füge einen Schlüssel ein und wähle ein Modell. Dein Schlüssel wird sicher im macOS-Schlüsselbund gespeichert und verlässt deinen Mac nur als die Anfrage, die du stellst."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Coach uses your own API key. Pick a provider, paste a key, and choose a model. Your key is stored securely in the macOS Keychain and never leaves your Mac except as the request you make."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "El Entrenador usa tu propia clave de API. Elige un proveedor, pega una clave y elige un modelo. Tu clave se almacena de forma segura en el Llavero de macOS y nunca sale de tu Mac salvo como la solicitud que tú haces."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Coach utilise votre propre clé API. Choisissez un fournisseur, collez une clé et sélectionnez un modèle. Votre clé est stockée de façon sécurisée dans le trousseau macOS et ne quitte jamais votre Mac sauf pour la requête que vous effectuez."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Il Coach usa la tua chiave API. Scegli un provider, incolla una chiave e seleziona un modello. La tua chiave è conservata in modo sicuro nel Portachiavi di macOS e non lascia mai il tuo Mac, se non come parte della richiesta che effettui."
          }
        },
        "ru": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ИИ-тренер использует ваш API-ключ. Выберите провайдера, вставьте ключ и выберите модель. Ключ надёжно хранится в «Связке ключей» macOS и отправляется только при выполнении вашего запроса."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "教练使用你自己的 API 密钥。选择一个服务商，粘贴密钥，再选择一个模型。你的密钥安全地存储在 macOS 钥匙串中，除了你发起的请求外，绝不会离开你的 Mac。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "教練使用你自己的 API 金鑰。選擇一個服務供應商，貼上金鑰，再選擇一個模型。你的金鑰安全地儲存在 macOS 鑰匙圈中，除了你發起的請求外，絕不會離開你的 Mac。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
