    "From the watch's wrist-temperature sensor during sleep, on Series 8 and later. Older models don't have the sensor, so it reads “not available” rather than zero.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Vom Handgelenktemperatur-Sensor der Uhr im Schlaf, ab Series 8. Ältere Modelle haben den Sensor nicht, daher steht dort „nicht verfügbar“ statt null."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Desde el sensor de temperatura de muñeca del reloj durante el sueño, en Series 8 y posteriores. Los modelos anteriores no tienen el sensor, así que muestra «no disponible» en lugar de cero."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Dal sensore di temperatura al polso dell'orologio durante il sonno, su Series 8 e successivi. I modelli più vecchi non hanno il sensore, quindi mostra “non disponibile” invece di zero."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "来自手表睡眠期间的手腕温度传感器，仅限 Series 8 及之后的机型。较早的机型没有该传感器，所以显示「不可用」而不是零。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "來自手錶睡眠期間的手腕溫度感測器，適用於 Series 8 及之後的型號。較舊的型號沒有這個感測器，所以會顯示「無法取得」而非零。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "From your nightly sensor": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Von deinem nächtlichen Sensor"
