    "It all stays on your strap and %@: no account, no cloud.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Alles bleibt auf deinem Strap und %@: kein Konto, keine Cloud."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Todo permanece en tu pulsera y en %@: sin cuenta, sin nube."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tutto resta sulla tua fascia e su %@: nessun account, nessun cloud."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "一切都留在你的手环和 %@ 上：无账号，无云端。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "一切都留在你的手環和 %@ 上：沒有帳號，沒有雲端。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "It is a picture, not a verdict": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Es ist ein Bild, kein Urteil"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Es una imagen, no un veredicto"
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "È una fotografia, non un verdetto"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "这是一幅图景，不是结论"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "它是一幅圖像，不是一個判決"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "It is not a substitute for a professional": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Es ist kein Ersatz für Fachpersonal"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "No sustituye a un profesional"
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Non sostituisce un professionista"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "它不能替代专业人士"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "它不能替代專業人員"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "It isn't held by the WHOOP phone app. Only one host at a time: close the app or turn off its Bluetooth.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Er wird nicht von der WHOOP-App gehalten. Nur ein Host zur Zeit: Schließe die App oder schalte ihr Bluetooth aus."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "No está retenida por la app de WHOOP del teléfono. Solo un anfitrión a la vez: cierra la app o desactiva su Bluetooth."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Non è trattenuta dall'app WHOOP del telefono. Un solo host alla volta: chiudi l'app o disattiva il suo Bluetooth."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "它没有被 WHOOP 手机应用占用。同一时间只能有一个主机：请关闭该应用或关掉它的 Bluetooth。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "它沒有被 WHOOP 手機應用程式佔用。一次只能有一個主機：請關閉該應用程式或關閉其 Bluetooth。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "It shows the shape of your heartbeat timing and a plain-language description of how steady it looked. It does not tell you whether anything is right or wrong.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Es zeigt die Form deines Herzschlag-Timings und eine klar formulierte Beschreibung, wie gleichmäßig es aussah. Es sagt dir nicht, ob etwas richtig oder falsch ist."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Muestra la forma del ritmo de tus latidos y una descripción en lenguaje sencillo de lo estable que se vio. No te dice si algo está bien o mal."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Mostra la forma dei tempi del tuo battito e una descrizione in linguaggio semplice di quanto è apparso regolare. Non ti dice se qualcosa va bene o male."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "它展示你心跳节律的形态，并用通俗语言描述其看起来有多平稳。它不会告诉你有没有问题。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "它顯示你心跳時序的形態，以及用平實語言描述它看起來有多穩定。它不會告訴你任何事情是對是錯。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "It's a notebook, not a lab. NOOP lines up the numbers you enter. It doesn't test, read, or judge them. Not medical advice.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Es ist ein Notizbuch, kein Labor. NOOP stellt die Zahlen, die du eingibst, nebeneinander. Es testet, liest oder beurteilt sie nicht. Kein medizinischer Rat."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Es un cuaderno, no un laboratorio. NOOP alinea los números que introduces. No los analiza, interpreta ni juzga. No es consejo médico."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "È un taccuino, non un laboratorio. NOOP allinea i numeri che inserisci, non li analizza, legge o giudica. Non è un consiglio medico."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "它是一个笔记本，而非实验室。NOOP 只是把你录入的数字排列对齐，它不检测、不解读、也不评判它们。并非医疗建议。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "它是一個筆記本，而非實驗室。NOOP 只是把你錄入的數字排列對齊，它不檢測、不解讀、也不評判它們。並非醫療建議。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "It's charged and worn. The sensor needs skin contact to wake.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Er ist geladen und wird getragen. Der Sensor braucht Hautkontakt zum Aufwachen."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Está cargada y puesta. El sensor necesita contacto con la piel para despertar."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "È carico e indossato. Il sensore ha bisogno del contatto con la pelle per svegliarsi."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "它已充电并佩戴。传感器需要接触皮肤才能唤醒。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "它已充電並戴上。感測器需要接觸皮膚才能喚醒。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "It's within about a metre of %@.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Er ist etwa einen Meter von %@ entfernt."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Está a aproximadamente un metro de %@."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "È a circa un metro da %@."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "它在 %@ 约一米范围内。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "它在 %@ 約一公尺範圍內。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
