    "Nothing here yet. Tap Enable Apple Health above to read your data live, or import a Health export .zip in Data Sources.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Hier ist noch nichts. Tippe oben auf „Apple Health aktivieren“, um deine Daten live zu lesen, oder importiere eine Health-Export-.zip unter „Datenquellen“."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Aún no hay nada aquí. Toca Activar Apple Health arriba para leer tus datos en vivo, o importa un .zip de exportación de Health en Fuentes de datos."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ancora niente qui. Tocca Abilita Apple Health qui sopra per leggere i tuoi dati in diretta, oppure importa un file .zip di esportazione Health in Sorgenti dati."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "这里还没有内容。点击上方的「启用 Apple 健康」以实时读取你的数据，或在「数据来源」中导入一个健康导出的 .zip 文件。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "這裡還沒有內容。點擊上方的「啟用 Apple 健康」以即時讀取你的資料，或在「資料來源」中匯入一個健康匯出的 .zip 檔案。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Nothing here yet. This sideloaded install can't read Apple Health directly. Import a Health export .zip in Data Sources, or turn on Shortcuts Export to bring your strap data into Health.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Hier ist noch nichts. Diese sideloadete Installation kann Apple Health nicht direkt lesen. Importiere eine Health-Export-.zip unter „Datenquellen“ oder schalte den Kurzbefehle-Export ein, um deine Strap-Daten in Health zu bringen."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Aún no hay nada aquí. Esta instalación por sideload no puede leer Apple Health directamente. Importa un .zip de exportación de Health en Fuentes de datos, o activa la exportación por Atajos para llevar los datos de tu pulsera a Health."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ancora niente qui. Questa installazione sideload non può leggere Apple Health direttamente, importa un file .zip di esportazione Health in Sorgenti dati, oppure attiva l'Esportazione tramite Comandi per portare i dati della tua fascia in Health."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "这里还没有内容。此旁加载的安装无法直接读取 Apple 健康，请在「数据来源」中导入一个健康导出的 .zip 文件，或开启「快捷指令导出」以将你的手环数据带入「健康」。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "這裡還沒有內容。此側載的安裝無法直接讀取 Apple 健康，請在「資料來源」中匯入一個健康匯出的 .zip 檔案，或開啟「捷徑匯出」以將你的手環資料帶入「健康」。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Nothing imported": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Nichts importiert"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
