    "Off, the coach answers generally and sends none of your metrics.": {
      "extractionState": "stale",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Aus, der Coach antwortet allgemein und sendet keine deiner Metriken."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Off, the coach answers generally and sends none of your metrics."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Desactivado: el entrenador responde de forma general y no envía ninguna de tus métricas."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Désactivé, le coach répond de manière générale et n'envoie aucune de vos métriques."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Off, il Coach risponde in modo generico e non invia nessuna delle tue metriche."
          }
        },
        "ru": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Выкл., ИИ-тренер отвечает общими рекомендациями и не отправляет ваши показатели."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "关闭，，教练只作一般性回答，不会发送你的任何指标。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "關閉，，教練只作一般性回答，不會發送你的任何指標。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Off: only your core metrics are shared, not your patterns or Lab Book.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Aus: Nur deine Kernmetriken werden geteilt, nicht deine Muster oder dein Laborbuch."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Desactivado: solo se comparten tus métricas principales, no tus patrones ni tu Cuaderno de laboratorio."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Off, vengono condivise solo le tue metriche principali, non i tuoi schemi o il tuo Quaderno di laboratorio."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "关闭，只分享你的核心指标，不包括你的规律或实验手记。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "關閉，只分享你的核心指標，不包括你的規律或實驗手記。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Off: the coach answers generally and sends none of your metrics.": {
