            "value": "讓手環進入配對模式，戴在你的手腕上並保持喚醒。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Put the strap on first. The deep stream is on-wrist only.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Leg zuerst den Strap an. Der Deep-Stream läuft nur am Handgelenk."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ponte la pulsera primero. La transmisión profunda solo funciona en la muñeca."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Indossa prima la fascia. Il flusso profondo funziona solo al polso."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "请先戴上手环。深度数据流仅在佩戴时可用。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "請先戴上手環，深度資料流僅在佩戴時可用。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Put your WHOOP 4.0 on your wrist and make sure it's awake.": {
