    "Watch for early-illness signs": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Auf frühe Krankheitszeichen achten"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Vigilar señales tempranas de enfermedad"
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tieni d'occhio i primi segnali di malattia"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "留意疾病早期迹象"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "留意疾病早期徵兆"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Watch your heart, live": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Sieh deinem Herzen zu, live"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Mira tu corazón, en vivo"
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Guarda il tuo cuore, in diretta"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "实时看着你的心跳"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "即時看見你的心跳"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Watches your resting HR, HRV, skin temperature and respiration against your own 28-day baseline. On-device and approximate: informational only, not a diagnosis.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Beobachtet deine Schlaf-HF, HRV, Hauttemperatur und Atmung gegen deine eigene 28-Tage-Basislinie. Auf dem Gerät und ungefähr: nur zur Information, keine Diagnose."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Vigila tu FC en reposo, VFC, temperatura de la piel y respiración frente a tu propia línea base de 28 días. En el dispositivo y aproximado: solo informativo, no un diagnóstico."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Monitora la tua FC a riposo, HRV, temperatura cutanea e respirazione rispetto alla tua linea di base di 28 giorni. Sul dispositivo e approssimativo: solo a scopo informativo, non è una diagnosi."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "将你的静息心率、HRV、皮肤温度和呼吸与你自己的 28 天基线进行比对。在设备本地运行且为近似值：仅供参考，并非诊断。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "將你的靜息心率、HRV、皮膚溫度和呼吸與你自己的 28 天基線做比對。在裝置上運算且僅為近似值：僅供參考，並非診斷。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "We compare today's resting heart rate and HRV to your own 30-day baseline. A higher-than-usual resting HR and a lower-than-usual HRV both push the score up, classic signs the body is activated. The combined shift is mapped onto a 0–3 scale: 0 is calm, 1.5 sits at your baseline, 3 is highly activated.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Wir vergleichen die heutige Ruheherzfrequenz und HRV mit deiner eigenen 30-Tage-Basislinie. Eine höhere Schlaf-HF als üblich und eine niedrigere HRV als üblich treiben den Wert beide nach oben, klassische Zeichen dafür, dass der Körper aktiviert ist. Die kombinierte Verschiebung wird auf eine Skala von 0–3 abgebildet: 0 ist ruhig, 1,5 liegt auf deiner Basislinie, 3 ist hoch aktiviert."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "We compare today's resting heart rate and HRV to your own 30-day baseline. A higher-than-usual resting HR and a lower-than-usual HRV both push the score up, classic signs the body is activated. The combined shift is mapped onto a 0–3 scale: 0 is calm, 1.5 sits at your baseline, 3 is highly activated."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Comparamos la frecuencia cardíaca en reposo y la VFC de hoy con tu propia línea base de 30 días. Una FC en reposo más alta de lo habitual y una VFC más baja de lo habitual empujan la puntuación hacia arriba: signos clásicos de que el cuerpo está activado. El cambio combinado se mapea en una escala de 0–3: 0 es calma, 1,5 se sitúa en tu línea base, 3 es muy activado."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "We compare today's resting heart rate and HRV to your own 30-day baseline. A higher-than-usual resting HR and a lower-than-usual HRV both push the score up, classic signs the body is activated. The combined shift is mapped onto a 0–3 scale: 0 is calm, 1.5 sits at your baseline, 3 is highly activated."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Confrontiamo la frequenza cardiaca a riposo e l'HRV di oggi con la tua linea di base di 30 giorni. Una FC a riposo più alta del solito e un HRV più basso del solito spingono entrambi il punteggio verso l'alto, segni classici di un corpo attivato. Lo scostamento combinato viene mappato su una scala da 0 a 3: 0 è calmo, 1,5 corrisponde alla tua linea di base, 3 è altamente attivato."
          }
        },
        "ru": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Мы сравниваем сегодняшний пульс в покое и ВСР с вашей личной нормой за 30 дней. Пульс в покое выше обычного и ВСР ниже обычного повышают оценку, это классические признаки активации организма. Итоговое отклонение переводится в шкалу от 0 до 3: 0, спокойное состояние, 1,5, ваша норма, 3, высокая активация."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "我们将今天的静息心率和 HRV 与你自己的 30 天基线进行比较。高于平常的静息心率和低于平常的 HRV 都会推高评分，这是身体被激活的典型迹象。综合的偏移被映射到 0–3 的量表上：0 表示平静，1.5 处于你的基线，3 表示高度激活。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "我們將今天的靜息心率和 HRV 與你自己的 30 天基線進行比較。高於平常的靜息心率和低於平常的 HRV 都會推高評分，這是身體被激活的典型跡象。綜合的偏移被映射到 0–3 的量表上：0 表示平靜，1.5 處於你的基線，3 表示高度激活。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "We could not take over this ring.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Wir konnten diesen Ring nicht übernehmen."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "No pudimos tomar el control de este anillo."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Non siamo riusciti a prendere il controllo di questo anello."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "我们无法接管这枚戒指。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "我們無法接管這枚戒指。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "We're not seeing any motion from your strap yet. Steps are estimated from your WHOOP's banked motion history, so your strap needs to sync that history before NOOP has anything to count.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Wir sehen noch keine Bewegung von deinem Strap. Schritte werden aus dem gespeicherten Bewegungsverlauf deines WHOOP geschätzt, dein Strap muss diesen Verlauf also erst synchronisieren, bevor NOOP etwas zu zählen hat."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Todavía no vemos movimiento de tu pulsera. Los pasos se estiman a partir del historial de movimiento guardado en tu WHOOP, así que tu pulsera necesita sincronizar ese historial antes de que NOOP tenga algo que contar."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Non rileviamo ancora alcun movimento dalla tua fascia. I passi vengono stimati dalla cronologia di movimento memorizzata dal tuo WHOOP, quindi la fascia deve sincronizzare quella cronologia prima che NOOP abbia qualcosa da contare."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "我们还没有看到你手环的任何运动数据。步数是根据你 WHOOP 存储的运动历史估算的，因此你的手环需要先同步该历史，NOOP 才有可供统计的内容。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "我們還沒有看到你手環的任何運動資料。步數是根據你 WHOOP 儲存的運動歷史估算的，因此你的手環需要先同步該歷史，NOOP 才有可供統計的內容。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
