          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Wear the strap overnight and these read from your nightly skin temperature.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Trage den Strap über Nacht, dann lesen diese aus deiner nächtlichen Hauttemperatur."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Usa la pulsera durante la noche y estos se leen de tu temperatura nocturna de la piel."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Indossa la fascia durante la notte e questi valori vengono letti dalla temperatura cutanea notturna."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "整晚佩戴手环，这些数据便会从你的夜间皮肤温度中读取。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "整晚佩戴手環，這些資料便會從你的夜間皮膚溫度中讀取。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Wear the strap, tap once, then let it sync and share your strap log.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Trage den Strap, tippe einmal, lass ihn dann synchronisieren und teile dein Strap-Log."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ponte la pulsera, toca una vez, luego deja que sincronice y comparte el registro de tu pulsera."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Indossa la fascia, tocca una volta, poi lasciala sincronizzare e condividi il log della fascia."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "佩戴手环，点按一次，然后让它同步并分享你的手环日志。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "戴上手環，點一下，等它同步後分享你的手環記錄檔。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
