    "You can change what you share any time in Settings › Health › Data Access & Devices.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Du kannst jederzeit unter Einstellungen › Health › Datenzugriff & Geräte ändern, was du teilst."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Puedes cambiar lo que compartes en cualquier momento en Ajustes › Salud › Acceso a datos y dispositivos."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Puoi cambiare ciò che condividi in qualsiasi momento in Impostazioni › Salute › Accesso ai dati e dispositivi."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "你可以随时在「设置 › 健康 › 数据访问与设备」中更改你分享的内容。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "你可以隨時在「設定 › 健康 › 資料存取與裝置」中更改你分享的內容。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "You can still bring your data in by importing a Health export from Data Sources. A build from the App Store, or one signed with a paid Apple Developer account, connects directly.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Du kannst deine Daten trotzdem hereinbringen, indem du unter „Datenquellen“ einen Health-Export importierst. Ein Build aus dem App Store oder mit bezahltem Apple-Developer-Konto signiert verbindet sich direkt."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Aun así puedes traer tus datos importando una exportación de Salud desde Fuentes de datos. Una versión del App Store, o una firmada con una cuenta de pago de Apple Developer, se conecta directamente."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Puoi comunque importare i tuoi dati importando un'esportazione di Salute dalle Sorgenti dati. Una versione dall'App Store, o una firmata con un account Apple Developer a pagamento, si connette direttamente."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "你仍然可以通过在「数据来源」中导入一个健康导出文件来引入你的数据。从 App Store 安装的版本，或用付费 Apple 开发者账户签名的版本，可直接连接。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "你仍然可以透過在「資料來源」中匯入一個健康匯出檔案來引入你的資料。從 App Store 安裝的版本，或用付費 Apple 開發者帳戶簽名的版本，可直接連接。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "You removed your active strap. Choose which paired band provides your live data, or leave none active and pair one later.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Du hast deinen aktiven Strap entfernt. Wähle, welches gekoppelte Band deine Live-Daten liefert, oder lass keins aktiv und kopple später eins."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Quitaste tu pulsera activa. Elige qué banda emparejada proporciona tus datos en vivo, o no dejes ninguna activa y empareja una después."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Hai rimosso la tua fascia attiva. Scegli quale fascia associata fornisce i tuoi dati in diretta, oppure non lasciarne nessuna attiva e associane una più tardi."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "你移除了你的活跃手环。请选择哪一个已配对的手环来提供你的实时数据，或者不设置任何活跃项，稍后再配对一个。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "你移除了你的活躍手環。請選擇哪一個已配對的手環來提供你的即時資料，或者不設定任何活躍項，稍後再配對一個。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "You said: %@": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Du sagtest: %@"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "You said: %@"
          }
        },
        "es": {
